headline: PSEG Foundation Celebrates 10 Years and Nearly $8M in Grants, Empowering Communities Across New Jersey and New York
summary: The PSEG Foundation celebrated a decade of community impact through its Neighborhood Partners Program (NPP), hosting a special event to honor more than 400 nonprofit organizations that have received nearly $8 million in grants since the program's inception. This year, the program set new records, with an 11% increase in applications and $1.2 million in total giving—a 20% rise from last year's $1 million.
